 And I always knew with Scott,

116
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:54,520
 we were gonna have fun, but no one was gonna die.

117
00:05:54,520 --> 00:05:57,760
 The problem was I'm tied up in the back of the truck

118
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:59,680
 and Scott's not there.

119
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:03,320
 And then they start to pull out on my driveway

