00:28:51,720 --> 00:28:53,640
 She shall not be moved.

602
00:28:53,640 --> 00:28:57,080
 God will help her when the morning dawns.

603
00:28:57,080 --> 00:28:59,280
 The nations rage, the kingdoms totter.

604
