 He burns the chariots with fire."

612
00:29:25,620 --> 00:29:28,240
 Okay, the second thing,

613
00:29:28,240 --> 00:29:30,700
 you want to fight anxiety in your life?

614
00:29:30,700 --> 00:29:35,700
 The second thing is you need to behold the works of the Lord.

615
00:29:35,700 --> 00:29:38,440
 Behold the works of the Lord.

616
00:29:38,440 --> 00:29:42,080
 So interesting in verse four, he says,

617
00:29:42,080 --> 00:29:43,760
 "So everything's shaking."

