00:30:18,740 --> 00:30:22,640
 but there is a river, a rushing wild river

636
00:30:22,640 --> 00:30:25,040
 that's flowing with life and vitality

637
00:30:25,040 --> 00:30:28,200
 that you can't see that's powerful

638
00:30:28,200 --> 00:30:31,240
 and it's flowing and it's working."

