 She turned six on Saturday.

742
00:34:27,720 --> 00:34:28,560
 I'm celebrating that.

743
00:34:28,560 --> 00:34:29,640
 I'm just thinking of my wife,

744
00:34:29,640 --> 00:34:32,260
 how grateful I am for her, thanking God for his grace.

745
00:34:32,260 --> 00:34:34,200
 And you know what didn't happen?

