00:34:40,960 --> 00:34:42,800
 and began to just, and gratitude.

750
00:34:42,800 --> 00:34:44,500
 Think of what God has done for me.

751
00:34:44,500 --> 00:34:46,360
 That's the first thing.

752
00:34:46,360 --> 00:34:47,960
 Remember what God has done for you.

753
00:34:47,960 --> 00:34:49,320
 Have a heart of gratitude.

754
00:34:49,320 --> 00:34:54,320
 The second though, is remind others around you of truth,

755
00:34:54,320 --> 00:34:57,120
