756
00:34:57,120 --> 00:34:59,120
 Here's what happens with anxiety.

757
00:34:59,120 --> 00:35:01,440
 So often you get tunnel vision

758
00:35:01,440 --> 00:35:03,500
 and all you can think about is you.

759
00:35:03,500 --> 00:35:06,720
 You literally are so focused on you.

760
00:35:06,720 --> 00:35:07,640
 What's wrong with me?

761
00:35:07,640 --> 00:35:08,480
 What's going on with me?

762
00:35:08,480 --> 00:35:10,320
 How do I fix me?

763
00:35:10,320 --> 00:35:14,100
 Something happens when we look up and we see other people.

764
00:35:14,100 --> 00:35:17,080
 I remember when I was a little guy,

765
00:35:17,080 --> 00:35:20,360
 grew up here for a few years in DFW

766
