00:35:33,180 --> 00:35:36,540
 I'm flipping out, like flipping out.

771
00:35:36,540 --> 00:35:39,680
 Something happened in fifth grade for me.

772
00:35:39,680 --> 00:35:42,040
 I remember I'm in class, fifth grade,

773
00:35:42,040 --> 00:35:45,240
 tornado siren goes off, I start flipping out.

774
00:35:45,240 --> 00:35:49,880
 And then I look over and I see my friend Tanner

775
00:35:49,880 --> 00:35:51,560
 flipping out more than me.

776
00:35:51,560 --> 00:35:53,680
 And I had the thought,

777
00:35:53,680 --> 00:35:55,920
 it was like a semi-rational thought for a fifth grader.

778
00:35:55,920 --> 00:35:58,200
 I was like, that's kind of crazy.

779
00:35:58,200 --> 00:36:00,700
 You know, like we're probably not gonna die.

