1036
00:47:39,520 --> 00:47:45,580
 there are some anxious thoughts that are beyond tornadoes

1037
00:47:45,580 --> 00:47:49,180
 and a night of no sleep.

1038
00:47:49,180 --> 00:47:52,760
 There are people in this room who have contemplated,

1039
00:47:52,760 --> 00:47:54,540
 I no longer belong on this planet.

1040
00:47:56,520 --> 00:48:00,120
 There are some who they literally can't even think

1041
00:48:00,120 --> 00:48:02,200
 rationally for a minute because their mind

1042
00:48:02,200 --> 00:48:04,160
 is racing so much.

1043
00:48:04,160 --> 00:48:06,620
 There are people who, God, they doubt your existence,

1044
00:48:06,620 --> 00:48:07,820
 they doubt your love,

1045
00:48:07,820 --> 00:48:10,080
 despite all the sermons that they've been in.

1046
00:48:10,080 --> 00:48:16,280
 That gnawing thought is wrestling them day and night.

1047
00:48:16,280 --> 00:48:22,680
 And yet, as we just read, the God of Jacob,

1048
00:48:22,680 --> 00:48:26,220
 the God of the wrestler is on my side.

1049
00:48:26,220 --> 00:48:30,960
 Lord, you don't promise that in this life,

1050
00:48:30,960 --> 00:48:33,560
 all the healing that we want will happen,

1051
00:48:33,560 --> 00:48:36,860
 but you do promise the Lord of hosts is with us.

1052
00:48:36,860 --> 00:48:39,820
 The God of Jacob is on my side.

1053
00:48:39,820 --> 00:48:46,280
 So God, be near, help us feel you.

1054
00:48:46,280 --> 00:48:48,720
 Lord, whatever it takes in our mind,

1055
00:48:48,720 --> 00:48:51,360
 fill us with your spirit such that your nearness

1056
00:48:51,360 --> 00:48:53,060
 is closer than our anxiety.

1057
00:48:53,060 --> 00:48:57,960
 And God, help us to say the hard but true words,

1058
00:48:57,960 --> 00:49:00,220
 you are God, I am not God.

1059
00:49:00,220 --> 00:49:05,240
 We love you and we trust you in Jesus' name, amen.

1060
00:49:05,240 --> 00:49:06,080
 Amen.

